Author: Parodium
Title: [ANN][ICO] Safein - A Single Sign-on Digital Identity Management Platform
Body: Project & Token Sale Launch Update;  Dear Safein Community  The last few months have been an incredible journey for Safein. In this time, our founders have met with literally hundreds of industry professionals and experts who have helped us deeply understand the potential of our project, and allowed us to truly consider the best path to realize our vision. Based on all of this experience and our projects for the future, we have decided to delay the start of token sale until Q3 2018.    We understand that this may come as a shock to our supporters, considering that we just took down the $250,000 grand prize at iCoin Summit, but this step was not taken lightly. We truly believe that in order to reach our full potential we need to really drive-home the benefits of our platform. To do this, we have agreements to provide KYC services to several ICOs, allowing us to prove the utility of our service and demonstrate our revenue generating model.  We would like to thank everybody for their support thus far and want to offer an additional 5% SFN bonus to all who have whitelisted by the 31st of May.  For the full details on why we have taken this step, please read our latest article;  https://medium.com/safeincom/project-token-sale-launch-update-7e0197cc8c90

We intend to protect your data using the most secure systems possible, this will not change regardless of your sign-in route. If you don't want merchants (or anybody else) accessing your data, then they will not have access to your data. We will not be marketing your data.  Quote from: momo on April 11, 2018, 07:31:50 PM You say that the use of safein will allow the stores to reduce the support team maintenance costs. How will this be achieved?  We will handle KYC procedures and provide a platform to connect merchants and clients, this reduces advertising costs, KYC operation and storage costs, and simplifies the overall customer to merchant experience.  Quote from: budrabut on April 11, 2018, 10:13:24 PM I think it's a good project to see the idea of this project, and also the promotional program being done, is there a bounty campaign on this project, and also how much is it allocated and for that?   There is a bounty campaign, please see the following;  https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=3037593.0  It will be extended until the end of June, current token allocation is 5,000,000 SFN, but this will be increased to compensate for the extension. Safein interacts in different business areas where it joins in all the areas and provides benefits to users both through online and offline. Safein helps in eliminating unwanted registrations and KYC procedures. Thus, Safein uses the entire all the crypto payment that can be performed on all the websites of e-commerce. However, Payment Service Provider will accept both fiat and crypto payments. Safein will solve all the problems by permitting all the users to pay for all the goods bought by them. Title: [ANN][ICO] Safein - A Single Sign-on Digital Identity Management Platform
Body: We are currently in talks with a number of potential partners. We agree that the gaming segment should be a priority for us, this is why our first major partnership was with Ultraplay.  Quote from: fgreg2692june on April 07, 2018, 02:20:24 PM If my data was used without my acknowledgement, will I be able to prove it providing any logs or reports taken from yr solution?  Your data will not be used without your permission, that is our entire concept. 3rd parties will not have access to your data without your consent.  Quote from: Dreadtrader on April 07, 2018, 02:38:18 PM Good afternoon. Will yr team check any documents manually or will the process be automated?  Currently documents are confirmed manually, however we are aiming to integrate with the world's leading automated ID verification service to switch to a fully automatic approach.  Quote from: sorrelin on April 07, 2018, 02:42:32 PM Some exchanges check the users’ data for months… Are u sure that they will agree to use yr solution?  All merchants/services using our platform will be subject to the same restrictions. We will not allow unauthorized access to your data, you will be in full control of who access your private information.

Author: Vladdirescu87
Title: [ANN][ICO] Safein - A Single Sign-on Digital Identity Management Platform
Body: Decentralized Wallet and Identity Platform Safein has Announced Pre-Token Generation Event, Starting 3rd of April 2018  Identity theft is a prevailing issue in the digital world of today with millions of IDs compromised around the world on a regular basis. Hackers use identity theft for a variety of illegal purposes, the most pressing of which is the misuse of money. Blockchain Technology has long been seen as a viable proponent of an eventual decentralized identity platform that can help overcome these challenges faced by companies, individuals and governments around the world.  Safein is a new blockchain-based digital currency wallet and identity system that is aiming to solve these persistent issues associated with living in the digital world. The promising startup has announced a pre-token generation campaign starting from 3rd of April, 2018.  Read the details in the article of Coinidol dot com, the world blockchain news outlet: https://coinidol.com/safein-announced-pre-token-generation-event-starting/

Author: Continuous
Title: [ANN][ICO] Safein - A Single Sign-on Digital Identity Management Platform
Body: Sometimes KYC procedures take several weeks to complete, this delay often leads to poor consumer adoption and reduced spending. Our solution massively improves the timescales between registration and first purchase, which is beneficial to both consumer and merchant.  Quote from: Mops on March 24, 2018, 10:55:10 AM Hello. Is your solution for undergoing of KYC by legal entities? Sometimes it takes even more time than usual verification.  One of our first goals is to acquire EMI licence. Feel free to read more about this here https://cointelegraph.com/news/startup-aims-to-make-online-shopping-easier-and-sharing-personal-data-safer and our whitepaper.  Quote from: martbruce on March 24, 2018, 12:13:21 PM Some stores complete verification in 24 hours. It seems to me that it isnt too long. Will they be interested in yr product?  Safein is providing multiple incentives to merchants ranging from discounts to less customer support required. Please read about merchant section in our whitepaper to get a full grasp of benefits they will get!  Quote from: omorbalsamhill1 on March 25, 2018, 06:37:11 AM Good afternoon. How many tokens will be available on the pre-ICO?  22.5M SFN tokens will be available on the pre-ICO (2,000 ETH hard cap).  Quote from: Veecker on March 25, 2018, 04:39:34 PM Good afternoon. It seems to me that not all site owners will be able to afford the transition to your decision. You can’t tell the exact cost of the transition, right?  Safein is providing multiple incentives to merchants ranging from discounts to reduced customer support required. Please read about merchant section in our whitepaper to get a full grasp of benefits they will get!  Quote from: dort on March 25, 2018, 06:28:26 PM Usually the site receives consent to the use of user’s data during registration, but your platform eliminates the need for registration. Don't you think that's a contradiction?  When registering for a website users will always be informed what kind of data is required by the website and it will be fully up to them whether to provide that information and continue with registration or not.  Quote from: robinzzon on March 25, 2018, 08:12:44 PM Good evening. Who can guarantee that the data, provided to your platform, won’t be used without my knowledge?  You will be in full control of your data and clearly see which website has access to which information of yours. Regarding data safety within Safein, we have top tier security advisors which will contribute with their knowledge from different fields. Feel free to check their credentials on our website.  Quote from: rdizza on March 25, 2018, 11:05:04 PM Hello. How do you plan to optimize the collection of users’ information? I want to register 1 time, and so I don't have to add anything to the form.  There will be multiple layers for providing information as each website requires different data. Feel free to read more about it in the whitepaper!  Quote from: shara on March 26, 2018, 12:27:41 AM As far as I know, the solutions similar to yours have already been created in the past but they didn’t become popular. In your opinion, what’s the reason?  This could be due to multiple reasons - it is worth mentioning that we do not see direct competition in the market and each project does something differently. We do not focus on what others are doing. Safein clearly sees a problem in the market and is capable of solving it.  Quote from: woodcoin on March 26, 2018, 12:30:03 AM Safein will completely exclude the possibility of bots and other fake accounts. Why don't you use this as your main argument in your marketing campaign?  Appreciate the suggestion! Will forward this to the team.  Quote from: zaqhig on March 26, 2018, 12:13:34 PM Hey everyone. How long pre-sale is going to be on?  The pre-sale will start on the 3rd of April and will end on the 16th of April or whenever the hardcap is reached.

Author: Continuous
Title: [ANN][ICO] Safein - A Single Sign-on Digital Identity Management Platform
Body: The Safein account won't need to be linked to anything. As soon as we obtain an EMI, we will offer IBAN account numbers to our clients. It will be as simple as transferring funds to other bank account of yours.  Quote from: rdizza on March 22, 2018, 05:33:43 PM Does it turn out that the scammers will be able to access all my accounts if  they access my account on the platform?  It won't happen because in order to do that, hackers would need to steal your phone and finger or your pass code as well.  Quote from: woodcoin on March 22, 2018, 07:15:56 PM Hey. Is it possible to integrate into the projects only a part of options of your platform? The fact that users forget their passwords loads my platform very much.  Yes, MVP is already there and feel free to check it out. However, when product is live it is going to be easily to customize according to clients needs.  Quote from: bars_kz on March 22, 2018, 08:39:07 PM The paces of growth of values of the platform and the tokens are very important for investors. Have you conducted an analysis allowing to estimate them?  Yes. Firstly we don't promote our tokens as an investment vehicle, but due to our unique token model where merchants by their commission not by spending, but by holding the token, supply of SFN tokens will go down significantly and due to our token benefits, price should go up by multiples compared to the ICO price.  Quote from: Veecker on March 22, 2018, 10:10:38 PM Good afternoon. Is your team already working on the project or will all the activities be carried out after the end of the ICO?  Our team has and is already working on the project. We already have a MVP out that you can try out.  Other than that, please check our roadmap!  Quote from: gazman on March 22, 2018, 11:38:03 PM Why did you decide to get the license in EU? Island states issue them much faster, and the check takes less time.  We are talking about EMI licence here which is needed to operate any wallet or payments business within the EU.  Quote from: national751 on March 23, 2018, 09:49:44 AM Good afternoon. Author: Continuous
Title: [ANN][ICO] Safein - A Single Sign-on Digital Identity Management Platform
Body: No payments functionality available yet. Only identity platform. Firstly we want to develop this part of the product since this is what is mostly needed by the crypto community at the moment. We are launching fully automated identity verification later this week.  As for Eidoo, it's just a wallet with an exchange inside it. This will be only a small part of our project. We are an identity management tool with a wallet, payments and exchange functionality. These two projects are just incomparable as we are a lot bigger solution to the whole ecommerce with a single sign-on solution and not just a wallet with a function to convert your currency.
